#BlueJ class context
comment0.target=TowerCC2Test
comment0.text=\r\n\ Propuesta\ de\ casos\ de\ prueba\ colectivos\ para\ la\ clase\ Tower\ -\ Ciclo\ 2.\r\n\ Todas\ las\ pruebas\ se\ ejecutan\ en\ modo\ invisible.\r\n\r\n\ Autores\:\ Madero\ -\ Valderrama\ (MV)\r\n\ Convenci\u00F3n\:\ accordingMVShould...\ /\ accordingMVShouldNot...\r\n\r\n\ @version\ 2.0\r\n
comment1.params=
comment1.target=void\ accordingMVShouldHaveHeightFourWithTwoCups()
comment1.text=\r\n\ Una\ torre\ con\ 2\ tazas\ debe\ tener\ altura\ 4\ (1+3).\r\n
comment2.params=
comment2.target=void\ accordingMVShouldHaveCorrectNumberOfItems()
comment2.text=\r\n\ Una\ torre\ creada\ con\ cups\ debe\ tener\ exactamente\ ese\ n\u00FAmero\ de\ elementos.\r\n
comment3.params=
comment3.target=void\ accordingMVShouldRestoreOrderAfterDoubleSwap()
comment3.text=\r\n\ Hacer\ swap\ dos\ veces\ entre\ los\ mismos\ elementos\ debe\ dejar\ la\ torre\ igual.\r\n
comment4.params=
comment4.target=void\ accordingMVShouldSwapTwoLids()
comment4.text=\r\n\ Intercambiar\ dos\ tapas\ debe\ funcionar\ correctamente.\r\n
comment5.params=
comment5.target=void\ accordingMVShouldAppearInLidedCupsAfterCover()
comment5.text=\r\n\ Despu\u00E9s\ de\ cover,\ lidedCups\ debe\ incluir\ la\ taza\ que\ fue\ tapada.\r\n
comment6.params=
comment6.target=void\ accordingMVShouldNotChangeNumberOfItemsAfterCover()
comment6.text=\r\n\ cover\ no\ debe\ cambiar\ el\ n\u00FAmero\ total\ de\ elementos\ de\ la\ torre.\r\n
comment7.params=
comment7.target=void\ accordingMVShouldReturnTwoObjectsInSwapToReduce()
comment7.text=\r\n\ swapToReduce\ debe\ retornar\ exactamente\ 2\ objetos\ (los\ dos\ a\ intercambiar).\r\n
comment8.params=
comment8.target=void\ accordingMVShouldReturnObjectsWithTypeAndNumber()
comment8.text=\r\n\ Cada\ objeto\ retornado\ por\ swapToReduce\ debe\ tener\ tipo\ y\ n\u00FAmero.\r\n
